cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

The paper discusses the use of deep learning in image reconstruction, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the instability of deep learning methods, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of algorithms and software to detect instability is also a topic in neural networks (cs.NE) and multimedia (cs.MM).
